          "name": "Mission",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>What We Build</h2><p>Multiplist Studios builds Intelligence Fields — living AI systems infused with your intellectual property. Not chatbots. Not automations. Co-intelligences that think alongside you, preserve what you know, and compound your expertise over time.</p><p>We started with a question: What happens to all the thinking you do between conversations? The frameworks you develop, the patterns you notice, the language you've refined over years of practice — where does it go when the chat window closes?</p><p>The answer was: it disappears. Every session starts from zero. Your AI doesn't remember what you've built together. We call this <strong>AI Amnesia</strong>, and it's the most expensive problem nobody talks about.</p>",
